Articles are the most trusted form of online advertising in South Africa, according to the 2022 Digital Marketing Report. The report found that online articles and reviews are also the most used marketing channel by business decision makers and consumers who are looking for information on products and services they are interested in. The 2022 Digital Marketing Report is based on a survey conducted in February 2022, in which 1,782 respondents took part. The majority of these respondents are South African business decision makers and professionals, who play a key role in a range of purchasing decisions: The graphs below highlight the key findings of the 2022 Digital Marketing Report. Click on the graphs to enlarge them. Online articles and reviews are by far the most popular marketing channel for business decision makers and consumers looking for information on products and services they are interested in. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-438474" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Channels.png" alt="" width="640" height="375" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Channels.png 2180w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Channels-600x351.png 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Channels-800x468.png 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Channels-768x450.png 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Channels-1536x899.png 1536w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Channels-2048x1199.png 2048w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Channels-1200x702.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Articles are the most trusted form of online advertising, according to business decision makers and consumers. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-438478" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022